OL,4,G1720FCome Dine with Me
OL,5,     GSurrey. Singing teacher Petrina
OL,6,     Ghopes that her experience
OL,7,     Gentertaining on cruise ships will
OL,8,     Ggive her evening the edge. And
OL,9,     Gher salted caramel chocolate
OL,10,     Gdessert serves up a surprise.
OL,11,G1750FCome Dine with Me
OL,12,     GSurrey. On the final night,
OL,13,     GGiovanni flies the flag for
OL,14,     GSicily with some family recipes.
OL,15,     GBut he has a tagliatelle tragedy.
OL,16,G1825FFour in a Bed
OL,17,     GNa'im and Sara host first at
OL,18,     Gtheir hotel in the breathtaking
OL,19,     GCumbrian countryside. But one
OL,20,     Gpair are too preoccupied with the
OL,21,     Gfurniture to care about the view.
